481
00:20:14,595 --> 00:20:16,329
But then when times
seemed darkest,

482
00:20:16,363 --> 00:20:19,032
she was there; she gave me
the strength and courage

483
00:20:19,066 --> 00:20:21,000
to fight for what I believe in.

484
00:20:21,035 --> 00:20:23,002
On behalf of Hollywood,

485
00:20:23,037 --> 00:20:26,673
we're dropping all charges!

486
00:20:26,707 --> 00:20:28,141
(cheering)

487
00:20:29,443 --> 00:20:31,811
(laughing)

488
00:20:31,845 --> 00:20:34,080
So what do you think, Lise?
Who are the good guys here,

489
00:20:34,114 --> 00:20:36,950
the media companies or
the Internet freedom guys?

490
00:20:36,984 --> 00:20:39,285
Well, both groups claim
their intentions are noble,

491
00:20:39,320 --> 00:20:41,955
but at the end of the day,
they're both trying to steal

492
00:20:41,989 --> 00:20:43,823
as much money as they can.

493
00:20:43,857 --> 00:20:46,092
So... everyone's a pirate?

494
00:20:46,126 --> 00:20:47,860
And the worst one of all is...

495
00:21:28,636 --> 00:21:31,437
(Seth Rogen laughing)

496
00:21:32,613 --> 00:21:34,614
Shh!

